const DesignBackground = () => {
  return (
    <svg
      className="designBackground"
      viewBox="0 0 500 250"
      width="500"
      height="250"
    >
      <defs>
        <linearGradient
          id="gradient-0-0"
          gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
          x1="249.832"
          y1="-15.031"
          x2="249.832"
          y2="198.782"
          xlinkHref="#gradient-0"
        ></linearGradient>
        <linearGradient id="gradient-0" data-bx-pinned="true">
          <title>Gradient 2</title>
          <stop stopColor="rgb(196, 150, 249)" offset="0.148"></stop>
          <stop stopColor="rgb(123, 65, 189)" offset="0.757"></stop>
        </linearGradient>
        <linearGradient
          id="gradient-1-2"
          gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
          x1="249.832"
          y1="-15.031"
          x2="249.832"
          y2="198.782"
          xlinkHref="#gradient-1"
        ></linearGradient>
        <linearGradient id="gradient-1" data-bx-pinned="true">
          <stop offset="0.148" stopColor="rgb(119, 0, 255)"></stop>
          <stop offset="0.757" stopColor="rgb(83, 24, 151)"></stop>
        </linearGradient>
        <linearGradient
          id="gradient-1-1"
          gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
          x1="326.598"
          y1="-8.553"
          x2="326.598"
          y2="170.018"
          xlinkHref="#gradient-1"
        ></linearGradient>
        <linearGradient
          id="gradient-1-0"
          gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
          x1="178.431"
          y1="54.704"
          x2="178.431"
          y2="254.675"
          xlinkHref="#gradient-1"
        ></linearGradient>
      </defs>
      <rect
        x="0"
        y="0"
        width="500"
        height="250"
        fill="url(#gradient-0-0)"
      ></rect>
      <path
        fill="url(#gradient-1-1)"
        fillOpacity={0.9}
        d="M 141.008 125.671 C 215.016 47.434 261.063 63.843 320.406 66.21 C 350.571 69.969 412.599 52.708 419.177 25.615 C 437.783 -23.864 479.163 -15.179 500.565 0.066 C 498.544 -2.017 501.896 149.682 500.717 173.209 L 26.941 224.339 C 34.029 227.714 148.891 129.425 141.008 125.671 Z"
      ></path>
      <path
        fill="url(#gradient-1-0)"
        fillOpacity={0.9}
        d="M 369.949 165.616 C 313.98 132.002 288.799 98.231 201.314 121.086 C 142.899 136.714 69.406 98.602 55.972 84.881 C 26.509 54.789 20.302 39.398 -0.524 31.346 L 0.201 250.893 L 370.362 229.112 L 369.949 165.616 Z"
      ></path>
      <path
        fill="var(--theme-white)"
        d="M -0.439 250.865 C 31.754 202.05 121.876 178.635 181.417 185.424 C 306.354 199.669 351.545 195.672 370.943 153.575 C 395.982 99.237 462.431 60.388 500.262 58.634 L 501.094 251.876 C 501.094 251.876 54.781 251.646 -0.439 250.865 Z"
      ></path>
    </svg>
  );
};
export default DesignBackground;
